data.description: Top Floor, Corner Unit - One-level living with Elevator access, full of south and west facing light in the heart of Bainbridge Island.  A rare opportunity. 100% walking score on Winslow Way near restaurants, Town and Country Market, coffee stands, weekly farmers market, galleries, museums, shopping and Ferry to Seattle. Fabulous View of Mountains and Bay from balcony.  Vaulted Ceilings, open floor plan with large gourmet kitchen. 2 bedroom, 2 full baths. Recent updates including new dishwasher,  AIR CONDITIONER, wine cooler. Private Elevator access from parking to unit. 2 coveted secure parking spaces with a large storage closet.
